# Phase-2 Implementation Plan

## Backend Plan (FastAPI)
1. Define Task data model
2. Maintain in-memory task list
3. Implement REST API endpoints
4. Validate inputs
5. Handle errors gracefully

## Frontend Plan (Next.js)
1. Create main task page
2. Display list of tasks
3. Add form to create tasks
4. Add controls to update/delete tasks
5. Sync UI with backend APIs

## Integration Plan
- Frontend communicates with backend using fetch API
- Backend runs on localhost:8000
- Frontend runs on localhost:3000

## Development Flow
Specs → Tasks → Backend → Frontend → Manual Testing
